# Refactor

## Svelte

- [ ] use [async](mdc:https:/github.com/sveltejs/svelte/discussions/15845#discussioncomment-13456944) branch
- [ ] use [@attach](mdc:https:/svelte.dev/docs/svelte/@attach) to replace Svelte Actions.
- [ ] use [<svelte:boundary>](mdc:https:/svelte.dev/docs/svelte/svelte-boundary)
- [x] debug with [@debug](mdc:https:/svelte.dev/docs/svelte/@debug)

### Iconify

- [ ] Move to iconify (https://github.com/unplugin/unplugin-icons/tree/main/examples/vite-svelte)
    - [ ] Select an [icon set](mdc:https:/icones.js.org) / https://iconify.design/ 
- [ ] Use [unplugin-icon](mdc:https:/github.com/unplugin/unplugin-icons/tree/main) and config for sveltekit

```js
import { sveltekit } from '@sveltejs/kit/vite'
import Icons from 'unplugin-icons/vite'
// vite.config.js
import { defineConfig } from 'vite'

export default defineConfig({
  plugins: [
    sveltekit(),
    Icons({
      compiler: 'svelte',
    })
  ]
})
```

